{"tid":157233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]私家車失控剷巴士站　候車長者3死傷","createTime":"2017-03-15T10:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T10:52:42.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38e328c9b912ac40444019f25ca9fb0bfcae9eed","tid":157233,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170315/bkncn-20170315042308017-0315_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170315%2Fbkncn-20170315042308017-0315_05011_001.html&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=a5fd9fdd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170315/bkncn-20170315042308017-0315_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170315/photo/bkncn-20170315042308017-0315_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170315%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170315042308017-0315_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=a71cbed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京方莊橋東昨日中午發生致命車禍，一輛私家車失控撞向巴士站，事件共導1死2傷。目擊者表示，死傷者全為候車的長者，一人更當場死亡。目前涉事私家車司機已被警方帶走調查，有消息指事件不涉及酒駕。<br />\n<br />\n據北京傳媒引述急救中心指，2名傷者皆為輕傷，1人為頭部有外傷，另1人則是右下肢外傷。而從網傳現場片段可見，涉事私家車前半部分剷上巴士站，路旁一個大型廣告箱玻璃被亦撞至粉碎，欄杆被撞斷，有傷者被撞後，嘗試仰起身體求助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}